casebody.data: In the matter of DISCIPLINE OF Daniel A. BECK. No. D-2838. Supreme Court of the United States Nov. 2, 2015. Daniel A. Beck, of Saluda, North Carolina, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
